<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id12279f4b-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on 44 U.S. Code, 1964 ed., § 245 (<ref href="/us/act/1895-01-12/ch23/s73">Jan. 12, 1895, ch. 23, § 73</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/28/616">28 Stat. 616</ref>).</p>
</note>
